name: scholarshipdb.net
overview:
scholarshipdb.net is a scholarship and research job search engine. The search engine employs state of the art technologies to collect latest information from various sources and present them to you in a single website.

We understand that scholarship hunting can be daunting and that’s why we present to you an intuitive and easy-to-use interface which allows you to search and narrow down your search in a few mouse clicks.

A keyword (e.g field of study, university, etc) is all you need to kick-off your scholarship hunt.
